594
00:38:19,329 --> 00:38:20,519
Spare me.

595
00:38:20,519 --> 00:38:22,440
I may be useful to Your Highness.

596
00:38:38,480 --> 00:38:41,199
Tell me what is so great about you.

597
00:38:42,960 --> 00:38:44,960
Otherwise, I'll chop you into pieces.

598
00:38:46,329 --> 00:38:47,400
I bet you know that...

599
00:38:47,599 --> 00:38:49,519
Chief Registrar Li trusts me.

600
00:38:49,960 --> 00:38:50,960
I know all his moves...

601
00:38:51,119 --> 00:38:52,239
better than anyone.

602
00:38:52,360 --> 00:38:53,440
During the battle at Wuding River,

603
