606
00:38:59,559 --> 00:39:00,559
Darn you!

607
00:39:01,039 --> 00:39:02,639
Nothing you say is pleasant to the ears!

608
00:39:03,159 --> 00:39:04,880
Are you trying to make me mad?

609
00:39:05,119 --> 00:39:06,159
Kill him!

610
00:39:06,159 --> 00:39:07,440
If Your Highness had any control over the situation,

611
00:39:07,599 --> 00:39:09,000
