626
00:39:50,559 --> 00:39:52,679
It's the perfect time to make peace.

627
00:39:52,809 --> 00:39:54,000
I know them really well.

628
00:39:54,239 --> 00:39:56,400
No one is more suitable for peace negotiations than me.

629
00:40:03,079 --> 00:40:04,480
The Eagle Army has been fighting for so long.

630
00:40:04,719 --> 00:40:07,039
However, everyone in Shuozhou still works together with high spirits.

631
00:40:07,719 --> 00:40:08,840
At worst,

632
00:40:08,840 --> 00:40:10,159
even if I can't persuade him,

633
00:40:10,289 --> 00:40:12,639
we can crush the morale of the people in Shuozhou.

634
00:40:12,809 --> 00:40:13,880
That's something...

635
00:40:14,360 --> 00:40:15,679
the Eagle Army can't do.

636
00:40:24,769 --> 00:40:26,400
Let's trust him for this once.

637
00:40:27,159 --> 00:40:28,880
Tie him up to my horse.

638
00:40:29,159 --> 00:40:30,159
Bring him to the battle.

639
00:40:31,289 --> 00:40:32,289
Make sure he lives.

640
00:40:34,440 --> 00:40:35,480
Yes, sir.

641
00:41:01,400 --> 00:41:02,480
